1. Moj *sin* je već odrastao. (My son has already grown up.)
2. *Sinovi* mog prijatelja su vrlo talentovani sportisti. (The sons of my friend are very talented athletes.)
3. Ne bih voleo da *sinovi* tvoje sestre upadnu u nevolju. (I wouldn't want your sister's sons to get into trouble.)
4. Kada su se *sinovi* vraćali kući, nisu videli da se neko uvukao u njihov stan. (When the sons were returning home, they didn't see that someone had sneaked into their apartment.)
5. Moja baka ima petoro *sinova*. (My grandmother has five sons.)
6. *Sinovima* je teško da pronađu posao u ovoj zemlji. (It's hard for sons to find a job in this country.)
7. Često se kaže da su *sinovi* slični ocu. (It's often said that sons are similar to their father.)
8. Njegovi *sinovi* su učestvovali u revoluciji. (His sons took part in the revolution.)
9. *Sinove* čeka dug put do uspeha. (Sons have a long way to go to succeed.)
10. Očevi se ponose svojim *sinovima*. (Fathers are proud of their sons.)